horbecke. {{ISBN|3-7995-4060-1}}\n* May, Johannes, 2000. ''Die himmlische Bibliothek im Pr\u00e4monstratenserkloster Schussenried'' (2nd ed.). (Marbacher Magazin, Sonderheft 87/1999). Marbach: {{ill|Deutsche Schillergesellschaft|de}}. {{ISBN|3-933679-27-3}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.kloster-schussenried.de/ Official website] {{in lang|de}}\n* [https://archive.is/20040619114355/http://www.bad-schussenried.de/sehenswertes/index_sw.html Bad Schussenried town website] {{in lang|de}}\n\n{{Swabian College}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1512]]\n[[Category:Premonstratensian monasteries in Germany]]\n[[Category:Monasteries in Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg]]\n[[Category:Imperial abbeys disestablished in 1802\u201303]]\n[[Category:Christian monasteries established in the 12th century]]\n[[Category:12th-century churches in Germany]]\n", "name_user": "Vami IV", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schussenried_Abbey"}
